                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </nav>
                <p style="color: black" class="copyright pull-right">
                    &copy; {{test | date: 'yyyy'}} <a style="color: black" href="http://www.cloudpointamerica.com">CloudPoint
                        Systems Inc</a>, made with <span style="color:red;font-size:20px"> &hearts; </span> for a
                    better Electronic Health Records
                </p>
            </div>
